# ============================================
# Product Directory
# ============================================
#
# This is where YOUR PRODUCT lives.
#
# Your product can be built with ANY technology:
#   - React + Vite
#   - Next.js
#   - Python + FastAPI
#   - Go
#   - Rust
#   - Whatever you need
#
# The factory/ folder contains AI tools (Arx-SDK) to help you BUILD
# this product. The product itself is technology-agnostic.
#
# Examples:
#
#   React app:
#     cd product
#     npm create vite@latest . -- --template react-ts
#
#   Python API:
#     cd product
#     mkdir src && touch src/__init__.py src/main.py
#
#   Next.js:
#     cd product
#     npx create-next-app@latest .
#
# The Dockerfile in the root will build and deploy whatever
# is in this product/ directory.
# ============================================
